              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "audit-logs", "entity", "Expense", "1"]
            },
            "description": "Returns the full change history for Expense with id=1.\nShows EXPENSE_CREATED → EXPENSE_UPDATED → EXPENSE_DELETED sequence.\n\nentityType values: Expense | Budget | RecurringExpense | User | Category\nRequires ADMIN role."
